{"tid":1235690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黑色三毛警示] 善用起底功能 懷疑所有網上消息","createTime":"2019-06-17T08:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T11:20:41.000Z","uid":179379,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"12bb6fbfb62d10ff4ab8cf1b95dc3bc42cd282b3","tid":1235690,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:16:11.000Z","msg":"正苦同狗依家已經轉咗策略<br />\n喺現實少咗狗清場，就代表佢哋放多咗人上網做三毛<br />\n<br />\n所以大家回post之前用多幾秒起一起樓主底<br />\n如見到下面幾類人，開一啲冇證據分化post / 假消息，又或者用好吸引你嘅標題 [突發] [急 人手置頂]，大家就要提高警覺<br />\n<br />\n1. 空白acc，唔一定係新acc，可以係佢一早申請咗備用<br />\n<br />\n2. 無限分化撚，開完和理非屌勇武，再開勇武屌和理非<br />\n<br />\n3. 之前不斷開假膠post<br />\n<br />\n4. 從來都唔開政治時事post，但突然有料爆<br />\n<br />\n呢類人唔代表佢一定會放流料，只係見到嘅時候提高少少警覺<br />\n<br />\n如果分唔到真偽，起埋頭5個reply嚟睇，好多時三毛都會幾個一齊推post<br />\n<br />\n如果發現三毛，記住個user name，下次唔好中伏"},{"pid":"2604631afb4f6069211d7f96e87f87dbf5277913","tid":1235690,"uid":179379,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:16:26.000Z","msg":"第二，懷疑全部網上所講嘅嘢，包括：<br />\n<br />\n1. Whatsapp / fb cap圖，你想要幾多我都可以整畀你<br />\n<br />\n2. 幾張相 + 一個故仔<br />\n<br />\n3. 所謂親身經歷<br />\n<br />\n4. 公海group講嘅所有嘢，你分唔到邊個係人<br />\n<br />\n對所有嘢有懷疑，唔好以為高正皮就一定真，先做fact check，fact check唔到就聽住先<br />\n當然唔排除佢係真實，但必須有戒心<br />\n<br />\n除非消息來自可信嘅朋友/user，或者有片有相，而片同相可以證實個消息係真"},{"pid":"a947a84216071b7971d8230a73874a90a408f166","tid":1235690,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:16:40.000Z","msg":"切忌推完/正皮先睇post"},{"pid":"fe86aa8fac85f78eedc11248edd431974c31fa09","tid":1235690,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:17:40.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"1a01bc9a74fbf77c9fe8fcdf054ce6eb74af82de","tid":1235690,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:18:05.000Z","msg":"Psuh"},{"pid":"a75a8fccf603af08b3d15b3de6d6c4de4badd0cf","tid":1235690,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:20:55.000Z","msg":"如果消息係假，你幫手鳩推，就會變幫兇"},{"pid":"8440afe329eeb3ed9f8063e83e2b241289e0881c","tid":1235690,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:21:21.000Z","msg":"Fact check<br />\nFact check<br />\nFact check"},{"pid":"e522181990cb80ee5031a8c91cc8f4a62542ef2a","tid":1235690,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:21:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"615fc01431727d979c87dc207de13b51dd72ff4a","tid":1235690,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:22:32.000Z","msg":"所有開乜撚&lsquo;新政府&rsquo;post基本上都可以當三毛"},{"pid":"87de965b8b02d812355eb6324d7705e343b56feb","tid":1235690,"uid":250979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:22:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a26212b8107a92f779745902494c8db9b2fa911","tid":1235690,"uid":179379,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"615fc01431727d979c87dc207de13b51dd72ff4a","tid":1235690,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:22:32.000Z","msg":"所有開乜撚&lsquo;新政府&rsquo;post基本上都可以當三毛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:30:05.000Z","msg":"嗰啲我當佢打飛機算<br />\n係啲捉鬼，帶風向互屌分化<br />\n<br />\n利申，屌民陣同律師割蓆，屌林高佬5比0，我覺得好正常，呢度相信好多人都俾民陣泛民出賣過<br />\n<br />\n但會有好多三毛利用呢件事，左一個屈屌人嗰個係分化撚，右一個扮勇武派屌晒所有和理非"},{"pid":"b74adf8d39101122d44014813f38992591f13456","tid":1235690,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:32:56.000Z","msg":"對"},{"pid":"3dedd6a24d9c56e5b186fb5fc2d2c1afab6ff89d","tid":1235690,"uid":179379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:40:18.000Z","msg":"記住，大家都好嬲，對5比0 / 捉鬼 / 割蓆行為一定唔滿意，屌係無可厚非<br />\n<br />\n而好多人都唔同意夜晚少人佔龍和，避免無謂犧牲<br />\n<br />\n兩邊意見唔同好正常，但唔代表和理非一定支持5比0，亦唔代表半夜佔路/衝就係鬼<br />\n<br />\n小心有三毛帶風向，扮勇武屌晒全部和理非，扮和理非屌人戴口罩/衝係鬼<br />\n<br />\n勇武和理非，缺一不可"},{"pid":"e6ec94c065db8ab8f427186dd6505371e421fc50","tid":1235690,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:43:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6320220661b9c43ccc4407ac7007dd5dbfe36f40","tid":1235690,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:57:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93553ee127a4ee655a166defc1f0f0975155cc6c","tid":1235690,"uid":196126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:11:18.000Z","msg":"一定要fact check"},{"pid":"a73d05f62e60e60d4b6d475d66696de760918f54","tid":1235690,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:31:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1d5b7ef7ec137ae82be6916b6f326ee7f9d34fe","tid":1235690,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:33:22.000Z","msg":"可否在此cap圖舉報"},{"pid":"4a079527bcbd61382abc0f4c5cea9144871c29c7","tid":1235690,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1d5b7ef7ec137ae82be6916b6f326ee7f9d34fe","tid":1235690,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:33:22.000Z","msg":"可否在此cap圖舉報"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:36:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得要將個意識推廣畀全部連登仔<br />\n得一兩個post舉報<br />\n但隔籬捉鬼分化已經推上熱門，人哋一定推熱門嗰個<br />\n所以要減少鳩推嘅人<br />\nFact check完先一齊推"},{"pid":"7120e2829cce166e32c7d22f4746baeb2e5fee4b","tid":1235690,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:36:38.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"768242ec3cf6b3080d25799d77202817390b86fd","tid":1235690,"uid":15693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:36:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f88e01956655790012242a02024579346663f331","tid":1235690,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7120e2829cce166e32c7d22f4746baeb2e5fee4b","tid":1235690,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:36:38.000Z","msg":"好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:37:07.000Z","msg":"大家努力"},{"pid":"c41cd3b2c640ac86de08c7905d5869c290b77033","tid":1235690,"uid":179379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T09:54:12.000Z","msg":"連登仔一齊提高意識<br />\n防人之心不可無<br />\n<br />\n不論網上定現場，都一定有鬼<br />\n所以所有你唔證實嘅嘢都唔好盡信<br />\n一定要fact check"},{"pid":"913c926f0656d2e77948b853a1aa4e0b3a87a998","tid":1235690,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:53:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05d8a2ddc824794a5f70c2342ac07c379a2d67c6","tid":1235690,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:54:17.000Z","msg":"嘥你五秒啫,起一起底"}]}